{"tid":2392031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宣明會／無國界醫生已經夠錢，請轉捐612","createTime":"2021-02-02T14:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T01:21:56.000Z","uid":381081,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"6011fd9bb8cb1bd3d4b1d235bb8cc03d74c18e22","tid":2392031,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:23:18.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4zohHr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4zohHr.jpg&h=94e62a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n【香港人每年捐近10億俾宣明會？！轉俾 612啦】<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好有錢，但都要用得其所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據宣明會同無國界醫生嘅年度報表，有近90% 嘅捐款都係來自香港個體（Mee就唔信全部都係藍絲）<br />\n<br />\n係時候提吓身邊嘅黃絲朋友停止月捐，集中火力捐俾「香港手足優先」嘅NGO<br />\n👉 612基金👈<br />\n<a href=\"https://donate.612fund.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdonate.612fund.hk&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=48d95d55\" target=\"_blank\">https://donate.612fund.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點樣CUT 宣明會？<br />\n可聯絡捐助服務部辦理終止助養手續，香港捐款及一般查詢 23942394<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點樣CUT 無國界醫生？<br />\n1️⃣熱線電話👉🏻長期冇人聽❌<br />\n2️⃣親身到辦事處👉🏻多人排隊❌<br />\n3️⃣電郵👉🏻得閒覆你❌<br />\n4️⃣取消銀行賬戶自動轉賬 ✅<br />\n<br />\n#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n支持我們開發App、推廣黃圈👉 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/36qF3rz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36qF3rz&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=2cc75397\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36qF3rz</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n#黃色經濟圈 #支持小店 #懲罰祭 #mee<br />\nFB📱 <a href=\"https://facebook.com/Mee.punishC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FMee.punishC&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=c6060673\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/Mee.punishC</a><br />\nIG 📷 <a href=\"https://instagram.com/mee_punishc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmee_punishc&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=edb9d296\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/mee_punishc</a><br />\nTG 📨 <a href=\"https://t.me/punish_Xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpunish_Xi&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=56fee22d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/punish_Xi</a>"},{"pid":"4f8eedd6319e53ba5a63d2278ab46205c3ea7e96","tid":2392031,"uid":40537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"28bca34c59b333364c7491dc236d49660d4da48b","tid":2392031,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70b455a8a130146bad2056d3ec384a6abdc0c91","tid":2392031,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:25:12.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"4e8ac9d6690c90b6822435291b708655909a248b","tid":2392031,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83fcf318901616963cfe2f5a4acd40515c1d64b","tid":2392031,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d56f7480aa5491ba429028a3d1d782fc41c697","tid":2392031,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc885486b20b246b866d315cf7a1174da15ad356","tid":2392031,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"