/>\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２：支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>支共無錢發難</ins><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">劇本２A：支共無錢發難引致世界大戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> &gt; <ins>香港獨立戰爭</ins><br />\n<br />\n[軍事小說] 習近平氏の希特拉化！英美德法荷日印澳同盟國形成！普京：依家局勢好似二戰前既30年代！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gCmQrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gCmQrS</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"b2c3a7ffa19ab3c52682dadf1d73565b8c77cf93","tid":2392031,"uid":316726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:13:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b2719230e06110cae591167f5903b5cd34d39c7","tid":2392031,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82210f21fe229c56be1bbec31f548e15238cdc8","tid":2392031,"uid":71090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/go